---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
import Link from "./ui/Link.astro";
---

<section id="cta" class="relative py-20 lg:py-24">
  <Container>
    <div class="surface-card relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 lg:py-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_14%_18%,rgba(27,97,201,0.08),transparent_28%),radial-gradient(circle_at_85%_22%,rgba(109,162,249,0.08),transparent_24%),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(249,252,255,0.94)_0%,rgba(255,255,255,1)_100%)]"></div>

      <div class="relative grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="accent-chip bg-[rgba(27,97,201,0.1)] text-[var(--color-primary)]">Desktop + Docs</span>
          <h2 class="mt-5 max-w-[13ch] font-display text-[clamp(2rem,3.6vw,3rem)] font-normal leading-[1.12] tracking-[0.01px] text-[var(--color-ink)]">
            从桌面端开始，先把 Agent 风险看清。
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-[34rem] text-[1rem] leading-7 tracking-[0.14px] text-[var(--color-gray-500)]">
            先跑一轮扫描，再决定要不要接着做权限治理和运行时策略。
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="data-pill">5 分钟完成首轮扫描</span>
            <span class="data-pill">桌面端与文档同一条路径</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row lg:flex-col">
          <Link href="/docs/aos-desktop/quick-start/" style="primary">
            快速开始
          </Link>
          <Link href="/docs/" style="outline">
            查看文档中心
          </Link>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
